GEOFF: Graph Export Object File Format
======================================

Status
------
This document is a work in progress and as such is currently incomplete.

Specification
-------------

EOL                      = CR / LF / ( CR LF )
LWSP                     = SP / HT
geoff-file               = geoff-line *( EOL geoff-line )
geoff-line               = blank-line
                         / comment
                         / descriptor [ 1*LWSP data ]
                         / composite-descriptor
blank-line               = *LWSP
comment                  = "#" CHAR
descriptor               = node-descriptor
                         / node-index-entry
                         / relationship-descriptor
                         / relationship-index-entry
data                     = <JSON object>
composite-descriptor     = "{" *LWSP descriptor-mapping *LWSP *( "," descriptor-mapping ) "}"
descriptor-mapping       = '"' descriptor '"' *LWSP ":" *LWSP data
node-descriptor          = "(" entity-name ")"
node-index-entry         = index-descriptor "->" node-descriptor
relationship-descriptor  = node-descriptor "-[" [ entity-name ] ":" entity-type "]->" node-descriptor
relationship-index-entry = index-descriptor "->[" entity-name "]"
index-descriptor         = "{" entity-name "}"
entity-name              = 1*( ALPHA / DIGIT / "_" )
entity-type              = 1*( ALPHA / DIGIT / "_" )
